         <pb facs="nyp.00074.001" xml:id="leaf001r" type="recto"/>
         <lg
              >
            <head type="main-authorial" rend="underline">The Pallid wreath.</head>
            <l>Somehow I cannot let it go yet, <add place="supralinear" rend="insertion">funereal tho' it is,</add>
            </l>
            <l>Let it remain back there on its nail suspended,</l>
            <l>
               With pink, blue, yellow, <add place="supralinear" rend="insertion">all</add> blanch'd, and the white<lb/>
               now gray and ashy,<lb/>
            </l>
            <l>One wither'd rose put <add place="supralinear" rend="insertion">years ago</add> for thee, dear friend,</l>
            <l>But I do not forget thee. Hast thou then faded?</l>
            <l>Is the odor exhaled? Are the colors, vitalities, dead?</l>
            <l>
               No, while memories subtly play—the past vivid<lb/>
               as ever;<lb/>
            </l>
            <l>
               For but last night I woke and in that spectral<lb/>
               ring saw thee,<lb/>
            </l>
            <l>Thy smile, eyes, face, calm, silent, loving as ever;</l>
            <l>
               
                  <subst>
                     <rdg varSeq="1">
                        <del rend="overstrike">No</del>
                     </rdg>
                     <rdg varSeq="2">
                        <add place="supralinear" rend="insertion">So</add>
                     </rdg>
                  </subst>let the wreath hang <subst>
                     <rdg varSeq="1">
                        <del rend="overstrike">yet</del>
                     </rdg>
                     <rdg varSeq="2">
                        <add place="supralinear" rend="unmarked">still</add>
                     </rdg>
                  </subst> awhile within my<lb/>
               eye‑reach,<lb/>
            </l>
            <l>It is not yet dead, <add place="supralinear" rend="insertion">to me,</add> or even pallid.</l>
            <closer>
               <signed rend="underline">Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
         </lg>
