            <p>My friends Can you use this in the <hi rend="underline">Critic</hi>? The price is $5 <add place="supralinear" rend="unmarked">&amp; 10 printed slips</add>—send me a proof wh' I will return immediately</p>
            <p>W W</p>
            <p>Jan 4 '91</p>
            <p>Camden <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#fl">Evn'g</unclear>.</p>
         </note>
